<br>
I am a level 56 (baron) mage and just got the epic. My guild is pretty much floored by what it can do. Due to my guilds average level we are still not world class in the dungeon delving department but nonetheless were floored by the epic.<br>
<br>
I went to OOT to seafury Island as an experiement and at 56 they are still light and dark blue to me. I pulled 6, that's right, 6 seafuries and the epic pet tanked them all! the only thing I had to do was cast Transon's about 4 times I think. All he had were two summoned swords, Muzzle and Burnout IV.<br>
<br>
That's pretty darn impressive by any standards because furies hit hard no matter what level you are.<br>
<br>
Voodini<br>
