 me.  Whether this is a bug or not I haven't a clue.  <br>
<br>
The epic pet is green to level 65, but he is an amazing damage machine for his level.  He is an equal pet in a duel against the 61 air (but mostly because both pets spear one another on the DS's) and can reap up the damage with all the procing he does.  <br>
<br>
If nothing else, you can use him to recover a little mana after a rez.  Either load and summon another rod before the rez or loot an unused orb from your corpse, summon pet, and reclaim.  <br>
<br>
It is still kinda hard to chain the epic pet, given the 20 second casting time to summon him, but he has his uses as a good backup or situational pet.  For mages below level 61, he is a clearcut choice over the other pets.  <br>
<br>
And of course the stats on the epic weapon itself rock unless you're in an uber guild getting the more impressive stuff out there.  In my opinion the epic is worth more than the status itself.  Plus it's one of those quests you can feel really good about accomplishing in the game, considering we have arguebly one of the hardest epics out there.   <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=222062">Booperbustle Tinkermeister</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
