<br>
So when I'm running around in some Dungeon, I'm saving my mana to heal the pet and clicking my nuke ring to pull mobs. Not having to redo the DS is a huge boon for that. (It may seem like a small amount of mana, but when you are constantly running, you don't regen much mana.)<br>
<br>
Of course, at level 52, this pet will carry me to 61 like no other tool available to any class in the game.<br>
<br>
It's also a huge status thing. I did it.<br>
